        },
        {
            "innerHtml": "The story of Rise of the Tomb Raider is okay, it can be predictable at times, but it does have some cool moments. The game ran extremely well on my PC looked visually brilliant throughout the game’s story. Long story short, as I said at the start, Rise of the Tomb Raider is another entry in the Tomb Raider series, nothing more, nothing less. I believe it is an above average-game due to the game’s brilliant parkour action sequences, of which are unfortunately bogged down by mundane Tomb Raider gameplay.",
            "tagName": "p",
            "attributes": [
                {
                    "name": "align",
                    "value": "justify"
                }
            ]
